lead_paragraph: Four members of the 'Aussie Stingers', Australia's women's Olympic water polo team, face 48 hours in medical isolation after suffering an attack of gastroenteritis on their way to Rio.

headline.print_headline: Waterpolo-Virus Hits Australian Women's Olympics Team
headline.main: Waterpolo-Virus Hits Australian Women's Olympics Team
